title: Crypto Analyst Predicts Ethereum ($ETH) Could Rise to $2,500, Amid Potential $XRP Breakout and $DOGE Decline
description: A popular cryptocurrency trader has recently revealed that he believes the price of the second-largest cryptocurrency by market capitalization, Ethereum ($ETH), is set to “easily” surge in the near future, and updated his outlook on altcoins $XRP and $DOGE.
